               <msContents>
                  <summary>The first volume of a Persian translation and commentary on the <title>Qur‘ān</title> by <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/90770167" key="person_90770167">Kāshifī, Ḥusayn Vāʻiẓ, d. 1504 or 5</persName>. According to the introduction the author had been engaged in composing a 4 volume elaborated commentary called <title xml:lang="ara-latn-x-Lc">Javāhir al-tafsīr</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar">جواهر التفسیر</title> for <name ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/22198747/" key="person_22198747">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Alisher Navoiĭ, 1441-1501</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">امیر علی شیر</persName>
                     </name>, when he interrupted his work after completing the first volume in <date calendar="#Gregorian" when="1492">897</date> to quickly prepare a simple translation entitled <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Mavāhib-i ʻalīyah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa">مواهب علية</title>. It was completed in two years between <date calendar="#Gregorian" from="1492" to="1494">897 and 899</date>.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_82-item1">
                     <author ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/90770167" key="person_90770167">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Kāshifī, Ḥusayn Vāʻiẓ, d. 1504 or 5</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">Ḥusain ibn ʻAlī Vāʻiẓ Kashifī, d. 910/1504</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" type="alt">حسين بن علی واعظ کاشفى</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">كاشفى، حسين واعض</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="alt" key="work_7245">Tafsīr-i Ḥusaynī vol. I</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7245">Mavāhib-i ʻalīyah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" type="alt" key="work_7245">تفسير حسيني</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_7245">مواهب علية</title>
                     <note>Vol. 1 <p>
                           <locus from="282v" to="282v">f. 282v</locus> The text end abruptly with the last phrase in Ayah 79, Surah XVII ( مقامأ محمودأ i.e. "A station of praise and glory" in Abdullah</p>
                     </note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa" type="beginning">بعد از تنهید قواعد مواحد الهی و تاسیس مبانی ثنا خخوانی حضرت رسالت پناهی علیه و علی اله و صبحه و صلواه ...</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa"/>
                     <listBibl>
                        <bibl type="text-relations">Volume 2 of the same work has class mark <idno>Persian MS 195</idno>.</bibl>
                     </listBibl>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
